lyrics:
[Verse]
In the woods we roam, with winter's chill
Setting up camp, on a snowy hill
Under moonlit skies, we gather 'round
A bonfire's warmth, the wilderness we crown

[Chorus]
Oh, winter camping, a frosty delight
Underneath the stars, we embrace the night
With laughter and stories, our spirits fly
In this frozen wonderland, our souls alight
